    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a quintessential analog performer powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. This example is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering power to the rear wheels via the factory M Variable Differential Lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings, providing the precise turn-in and feedback characteristic of this chassis. While the finish shows minor road wear consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain remains in peak operating condition with strong compression and a linear pull to the 8,000 RPM redline.",
      "price": 33500.0,
